OL,3,CStarmer should resign for 'shameful
OL,4,Crole' in appointment of Mandelson `
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn
OL,8,Fhas called for the Prime Minister to
OL,9,Fresign over his "shameful role" in the
OL,10,Fappointment of Peter Mandelson.
OL,12,FIt comes as Sir Keir Starmer is set to
OL,13,Fface the scrutiny of MPs in a
OL,14,Fstatement to Parliament on Monday over
OL,15,Freports that the former US ambassador
OL,16,Fwas appointed despite failing vetting
OL,17,Ffor the role.
OL,19,FMr Flynn has urged Scots to vote SNP
OL,20,Fto "show Keir Starmer the door" after
OL,21,Fall "the lies and broken promises".
OL,26,@qD@QOUqD@_O]|D@DOU|D@_O]}D@EOU}D@bO]
