OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer should resign for 'shameful
OL,4,Crole' in appointment of Mandelson `
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FHe said: "On 7th May, people in
OL,8,FScotland can vote SNP to sack Keir
OL,9,FStarmer and secure a fresh start with
OL,10,Findependence.
OL,12,F"It's clear Keir Starmer has no
OL,13,Fintention of doing the honourable
OL,14,Fthing and resigning over his shameful
OL,15,Frole in the Peter Mandelson scandal `
OL,16,Fbut voters in Scotland can show him
OL,17,Fthe door by voting SNP on 7th May.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOU
