OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer should resign for 'shameful
OL,4,Crole' in appointment of Mandelson `
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,F"The political reality is ` Keir
OL,8,FStarmer will use every vote for the
OL,9,FLabour Party as an endorsement to
OL,10,Fcling onto power and deny people in
OL,11,FScotland a choice over our future in
OL,12,Fan independence referendum."
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was sacked last year,
OL,15,Fless than a year into the job, after
OL,16,Fdetails of his association with the
OL,17,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein
OL,18,Femerged in files published by the US
OL,19,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@\O]
