OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer should resign for 'shameful
OL,4,Crole' in appointment of Mandelson `
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FThe Foreign Office has been blamed for
OL,8,Fclearing the peer in January 2025 to
OL,9,Fbegin as US ambassador, despite him
OL,10,Ffailing a secure vetting process.
OL,12,FThe Prime Minister has said he was
OL,13,F"absolutely furious" and described the
OL,14,Ffailure to inform him as "staggering".
OL,16,FSir Olly Robbins, who was only weeks
OL,17,Finto his job as Foreign Office
OL,18,Fpermanent secretary at the time, was
OL,19,Fsacked on Thursday as he had lost the
OL,20,Fconfidence of Sir Keir and Foreign
OL,21,FSecretary Yvette Cooper.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@TO]vD@ZOUvD@eO]
