OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776643375
OL,3,CStarmer should resign for 'shameful
OL,4,Crole' in appointment of Mandelson `
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,F"The constant chaos and soaring cost
OL,8,Fof living under Westminster control,
OL,9,Fshows why Scotland needs the fresh
OL,10,Fstart of independence and full control
OL,11,Fover our huge energy wealth to lower
OL,12,Fbills, protect our NHS and build a
OL,13,Ffairer, prosperous future.
OL,15,F"That is what the SNP is offering on
OL,16,F7th May."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUxD@IO]
