OL,3,CStarmer should resign for 'shameful
OL,4,Crole' in appointment of Mandelson `
OL,5,CFlynn
OL,7,FScottish Labour deputy leader Jackie
OL,8,FBaillie said: "Once again the SNP is
OL,9,Ftrying to deflect attention elsewhere
OL,10,Fbecause it cannot defend its own
OL,11,Fshameful record in government in
OL,12,FScotland.
OL,14,F"This election is about Scotland's
OL,15,Fgovernment, our NHS, our schools, our
OL,16,Flocal services, our community safety
OL,17,Fand our transport system ` all of
OL,18,Fwhich have been run into the ground by
OL,19,Fan incompetent and out of touch SNP
OL,20,Fgovernment.
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@AOU
